Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
66-68 Cubitt Street provides tenants with premium A grade office space in creative Cremorne. This recently constructed office building has been completed with the finest finishes; polished concrete flooring, outdoor green spaces and crisp LED lighting. The building is serviced with its own basement car parking which is easily accessible through a Cubitt Street entrance.

With an acute focus on detail, this brand new office space has provided an office building that will enhance the existing Cremorne landscape whilst drawing from the industrial history of the area.

It is located within the boutique Cremorne precinct and it's 1.5km within walking distance to Melbourne's CBD. Cremorne is well serviced by several train stations, the close by tram routes of Swan St and Church St and Bus route of Punt Road.

In close proximity to Citylink, the airport and the Monash Freeway one minute from the door. Not to mention the bike-friendly paths nearby.

•	Level 2 provides a self-contained tenancy of 245sqm with private bathrooms, shower, large boardroom and smaller meeting room.
CBRE are please to bring to market 28 Stephenson Street - one of Cremorne's best warehouse conversions, housing some of Melbourne's most innovative businesses in Taboo and The Monkeys.

-	Flexible interconnecting floors with substantial voids

CBRE is thrilled to present an exceptional office leasing opportunity in the epicentre of Cremorne’s technology and innovation precinct.

The highly anticipated Capital Cremorne on 167 Cremorne Street is a building specifically designed to improve the corporate 9 to 5. It overlooks the Yarra and is only 10 minutes from the CBD, easily accessible by train, tram and Melbourne’s picturesque cycling trails and riverside walks.

Outside, Swan Street and Church Street’s dining and entertainment options are endless - with some of Melbourne’s sought-after cafes, bars and restaurants at the doorstep. Inspiration will also flourish, as you’ll be surrounded by industry giants from Amazon to MYOB and Seek.

Inside, Capital Cremorne’s design addresses both form and function with flexible floor plates and interconnecting floors to suit any configuration. A multitude of airy communal spaces feature vertical gardens and an abundance of natural light, encouraging socialisation and a healthier take on collaboration.
The day to day workplace culture is further enhanced by cutting-edge end-of-trip facilities and a refurbished ground floor lobby for that striking first impression.

For further information and to register your interest, contact your exclusive leasing agents at CBRE.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: THE NEW WORLD OF WORK HAS ARRIVED.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: THE BEST STANDALONE OFFICE AVAILABLE IN CREMORNE

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located in one of Melbourne’s most sought after suburbs 42-44 Stephenson Street provides a truly unique opportunity for a free standing office to call your own.

Perfectly positioned minutes from Swan Street, this property boasts all the features that the tenants of today are after. Features include the high ceilings, exposed services, flexible storage, floor coverings of timber & polished concrete, great natural light and multiple outdoor entertainment areas.

• 500* sqm of NLA
• Small warehouse/storage component
• Two street frontages
• 3-4 car spaces
• 2 outdoor areas
• Partial fit out in place

Please call Josh or Anthony to arrange an inspection.
